=====================
BULLISH SETUP — BB BUY
======================

The probability improves as more conditions are satisfied.

WEEKLY (TIDE)

• Bollinger Band challenged on upside
(Price touches or closes near upper band)

• RSI > 60

DAILY (WAVE)

• Bollinger Band challenged on upside

• RSI > 60

HOURLY (RIPPLE) — Trigger Conditions

All must be satisfied:

1. Lower Bollinger Band downside challenge failed 

2. Heikin Ashi colour change from Red to Green

3. RSI > 40
   (Best when crossing above 60)

OPTIONS OI CONFIRMATION (BULLISH)

Use nearest expiry options.

Conditions:

• ITM CE OI decreasing → Short covering
• ATM CE OI decreasing → Short covering
• ATM PE OI increasing → Short buildup

FUTURES CONFIRMATION

• Price increasing AND OI increasing → Long buildup

If aligned → Strong Bullish confirmation.

Generate:

BB BUY Signal

