OPTIONS DATA REQUIREMENT
========================

For each signal, capture:

• ATM strike price
• ITM strike price
• CE OI change (%)
• PE OI change (%)
• OI absolute change
• Futures OI change (%)
• Futures buildup type (Long / Short / Short Covering / Long Unwinding)

Calculate OI percentage change:

OI % Change = (Current OI − Previous OI) / Previous OI × 100

